                %p
                  There were a couple of disruptions during the length
                  of the project - laptop hardware failure and a short
                  period of recuperation after illness - but Arzoo was
                  able to recover from these setbacks to complete most
                  of the planned work (mainly we didn't get into extra
                  items and stretch goals like short video tutorials).

