            %h3 Summary
            %p
              An excellent result for the Performance Co-Pilot project.
            %p
              We have a great set of short guides getting new users of
              the software able to solve problems immediately, and to
              learn more quickly about the wider set of PCP tools.
            %p
              We introduced consistency into all Tutorials and Guides
              across the project, by using a single readthedocs.io
              landing page for all PCP guides (same location, format,
              look-and-feel).
              Each new guide we add now will be incorporated into the
              set we've established during this project.
            %p
              In terms of what we'd do differently next time, perhaps
              a focus on getting video tutorials and animated console
              examples integrated earlier on would have helped us to
              get content suited to that medium using it more instead
              of running out of time to explore that at the end.
            %p
